headline: Alphabet (GOOGL) Stock in Focus After Truist Boosts Price Target on Search Dominance
summary: Alphabet Inc. (NASDAQ:GOOGL) is one of the AI Stocks in Focus on Wall Street. On September 22, Truist reiterated the stock as “Buy” and raised its price target to $285 per share from $225. Analysts remain positive on the stock highlighting that Google still controls 90% of the Search market despite new Gen-AI platforms growing in […]
